schemacrawler.schema

Class TableType

  • java.lang.Object
    • schemacrawler.schema.TableType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<TableType>

    public final class TableType
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<TableType>
    Represents a type of table in the database. Examples could be a base table, a view, a global temporary table, and so on. The table type name is case-sensitive, as it is known to the database system. However, string comparisons are case-insensitive.
